The world 's best golfers gathered on the eve of the Masters on Thursday to take on a nine-hole course , as part of the Par 3 Contest .
Tiger Woods showed up to the event at the Augusta National Golf Club in Augusta , Georgia , with his two children , Sam , 8 , and Charlie , 6 , and his girlfriend Lindsey Vonn .
Vonn 's ensemble was in stark contrast to the white jumpsuits .